item.title: IOS Build Note for Unity 2019 Vuforia
item.description: 前言 Unity 2019.2.11f1 Vuforia 8.5.9 iOS Build and Run Error ld: library not found for -liPhone-lib clang: error: linker command failed with exit code 1 (use -v to see invocation) Solution - iOS Build and Run Error Build Setting -> Search Paths -> Library Search Paths 移除 "$(SECROOT)" 參數 iOS Archive Error ld: warning: ignoring file ... building for iOS-armv7 but attempting to link with file built for iOS-arm64.
